overview: SmartData Partner is a trusted brand and one of the fastest growing B2B market intelligence, web research and data entry firm as well as a partner to many of the successful start-ups and small and mid sized businesses throughout the globe. Technology and Web 2.0 startups as well as emerging companies and consulting firms turn to SmartData Partner for web research services, customer support and data entry services that enhances their strategic decision making and day-to-day knowledge processes.
